    "Through improvements in the network structure and information processing modes of the YOLOv8x-pose model, our method achieves breakthroughs in accuracy indicators.",
    "In future work, we will attempt more improvement designs based on these foundations to streamline the model structure and improve the model's inference speed.",
    "This may include incorporating recent technologies such as ReXNet 7 and PAGCP pruning 57.",
    "Additionally, we also consider the application of the designed CCAM attention mechanism to other tasks such as image segmentation and object tracking.",
